channel.title: Please help
channel.description: I have had a server for a while then i lost interest but now im back into hosting my server and people cannot log on i dont know why it says when i run the .bat file that the server is up and running and i have no-ip running and my ports are open but when i try to register my server on the server status page it says server is offline. i asked some friends to join and it said error connecting to server. I could play by myself in the server though. please help
